<paragraph blockId="12.[189,1398,1272,1369]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
This genus is similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="Dietrich &amp; Magalhães &amp; Takiya, 2020" authorityName="Dietrich &amp; Magalhães &amp; Takiya" authorityYear="2020" box="[486,634,1273,1298]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Punctijassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
